{
  "stem": "5810.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You had to go into a vestibule.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The store would have been a right door to go into the store.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But if you continued down that vestibule you would go into the backyard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it is in that backyard that I had buried the money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so to go there, in a backyard, it wasn't necessary to enter the store, which had a closed door, because they wanted to close the door from the residents of the house.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at night, and after hours, where the front door on the street was always open, because it was a store, I was able to enter that, and make sure that the store doors were closed.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I wouldn't be uncovered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And go in the backyard, take out one, and come on out again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a time, however, where Fernand had followed me, because he had seen that I had done that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he watched me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he came out and confronted me with that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And although he was-- played with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wasn't necessarily my friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He called me dirty Jew many times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He, as a kid that age, would do at the time, he says, you know, if you don't do what I tell you to do, I will tell on you.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that scared me to no end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course what he had me do for the rest of the time that I was with the Barniche is his homework.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Any studies that he had to do, anything that his father and mother had told him to do, became my duties.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
